title: CMU Neural Nets for NLP 2017 (23): Debugging Neural Nets for NLP
description:
This lecture (by Graham Neubig) for CMU CS 11-747, Neural Networks for NLP (Fall 2017) covers:

* Diagnosing your Problem
* Debugging Training Time Problems
* Debugging Decoding Time Problems
* Combatting Overfitting
* Dealing with Loss/Eval Disconnect

Slides: http://phontron.com/class/nn4nlp2017/assets/slides/nn4nlp-23-debugging.pdf

Previous Video: https://youtu.be/rOiXjukeHSw
Next Video: https://youtu.be/4AQbrT-GD2k

See more details of the class here: http://phontron.com/class/nn4nlp2017/
